22:41.661 --> 22:45.496
Oh, forest, you break my heart.

22:45.498 --> 22:50.534
Oh, we still love you,
Tedi, just from far away.

22:51.269 --> 22:53.170
Like a fine work of art.

22:53.838 --> 22:56.173
Yeah, something like that.

22:57.409 --> 23:00.277
I'm upgrading your
workstations with the new Imacs.

23:00.279 --> 23:02.780
Retina display, flash
drives, the whole deal.

23:02.782 --> 23:04.381
Yes.

23:04.383 --> 23:06.050
I thought you'd like that.

23:06.052 --> 23:07.050
What about storage?

23:07.052 --> 23:09.687
Um, I'll have to look
into it, but storage is cheap.

23:09.689 --> 23:11.755
It shouldn't be a problem
getting it authorized.

23:12.223 --> 23:14.458
Hey, uh, what about
loosening up Websense?

23:14.460 --> 23:16.660
