hung above the porch.

24:21.293 --> 24:23.460
The old man staggered back.

24:23.462 --> 24:27.331
Shot twice, once in the neck
and the other in his chest.

24:29.434 --> 24:31.535
The dark figure rose
up onto his horse

24:32.070 --> 24:34.538
