disappearing into the night.

24:35.674 --> 24:37.608
Friends rushed to
the old man's aid,

24:37.610 --> 24:39.877
but it was already too late.

24:41.646 --> 24:44.415
The first shot had bored
a quarter sized hole.

24:44.417 --> 24:45.449
Now's your chance.

24:45.451 --> 24:46.417
To a chamber...

24:46.419 --> 24:48.085
What the hell are
you talking about?

24:48.087 --> 24:50.754
Chicks get super turned
on when they're scared.

24:51.823 --> 24:53.257
Like you would know.

24:53.259 --> 24:53.757
Trust me.

24:53.759 --> 24:58.162
Both times I scored the chick
was either drunk or scared.

24:58.430 --> 25:00.364
I think one of the
times she was both.

25:04.469 --> 25:05.636
Alright.

25:05.638 --> 25:07.137
Hey, hey, Zac?

25:07.139 --> 25:08.706
Just in case.

25:09.274 --> 25:10.474
Thanks, Tedi.

25:10.476 --> 25:11.642
Do you guys mind?

25:11.644 --> 25:12.142
No.

25:12.144 --> 25:14.812
Sorry. It was just getting
really good, Dale.

25:14.814 --> 25:16.547
Please continue.

25:17.048 --> 25:17.781
Thanks.

25:17.783 --> 25:22.653
Now as I was saying,
so much blood

25:22.655 --> 25:26.457
poured from the old man's
wounds that a thick pool

25:26.459 --> 25:28.358
formed underneath his head.

25:29.627 --> 25:30.694
He coughed once.

25:32.664 --> 25:33.797
And then again,

25:33.799 --> 25:37.101
the second being
a hideous gurgling

25:37.103 --> 25:39.470
sound as though
two invisible hands

25:39.472 --> 25:42.740
were choking the old
man to death,

25:43.441 --> 25:45.876
squeezing the very
life out of him.

25:47.245 --> 25:49.613
The sound sent a shiver
up the spines of everyone

25:49.615 --> 25:55.285
who heard the old man's
last dying breath.

26:05.096 --> 26:06.130
