26:42.667 --> 26:45.536
I'm a 'two buck
Chuck' type of girl.

26:50.475 --> 26:51.742
You okay?

26:52.410 --> 26:53.644
Yeah.

26:53.646 --> 26:54.745
I'm all right.

26:56.447 --> 26:57.247
No.

26:57.249 --> 26:58.549
There's something wrong.

26:59.050 --> 27:00.484
I see it in your eyes.

27:00.486 --> 27:01.351
Oh.

27:01.820 --> 27:03.821
You can read my
eyes now, can you?

27:03.823 --> 27:04.558
Yeah. I can.

27:05.456 --> 27:07.758
I bet you can't even tell
me what color they are.

27:09.828 --> 27:10.328
Well?

27:19.839 --> 27:21.471
<i>They are brown.</i>

27:21.473 --> 27:23.106
I know. I'm just
messing with you.

27:23.108 --> 27:25.442
