he's an asshole,

27:37.122 --> 27:38.455
but you'll get to used to it.

27:38.457 --> 27:38.955
No it's not.

27:38.957 --> 27:41.458
He once threw a girl
down a flight of stairs.

27:41.460 --> 27:44.828
Well, I'm sure he
had good reason to.

27:44.830 --> 27:46.330
Yeah, he did.

27:47.232 --> 27:49.233
Because she wouldn't
sleep with him.

27:49.235 --> 27:50.267
That will do it.

27:51.103 --> 27:52.469
That is not funny.

27:52.471 --> 27:53.437
That is...

27:53.439 --> 27:55.072
Why, why are you laughing?

27:55.074 --> 27:56.807
