27:56.809 --> 27:58.141
I see that.

27:58.443 --> 28:00.110
Damn you, Zac.

28:00.645 --> 28:03.046
Why do you always have
this messed up way

28:03.048 --> 28:04.715
of making me feel better?

28:05.416 --> 28:07.150
