28:09.120 --> 28:11.154
Are you going to tell me
what's wrong?

28:12.056 --> 28:14.892
Rita's not back yet.

28:15.660 --> 28:16.894
Are you sure?

28:16.896 --> 28:21.331
I thought she was just avoiding
Dale's tale of the occult in there.

28:21.633 --> 28:23.300
I'm pretty sure, Zac.

28:23.302 --> 28:25.135
She's been gone all day.

28:26.437 --> 28:28.105
Have you told Dale?

28:28.107 --> 28:29.172
No.

28:29.240 --> 28:31.541
I didn't want to spoil his fun.

28:31.743 --> 28:33.510
A whole hell of a lot of fun.

28:36.214 --> 28:37.748
Should we go back in?

28:38.583 --> 28:39.750
If we have to.

28:46.724 --> 28:49.726
From that day on the servants
couldn't keep the porch clean.

28:51.262 --> 28:53.463
Every few weeks a
damp pool of blood

28:53.465 --> 28:57.734
would appear in the same spot
where the old man had died.

28:58.670 --> 29:00.671
They tried repainting
the porch several times,

29:00.673 --> 29:04.107
but the blood stain would
always bleed through.

29:05.643 --> 29:07.778
One night one of the
servants saw something

29:07.780 --> 29:09.279
that caused him to go mad.

29:11.449 --> 29:14.451
Folks said that the
house was haunted

29:14.453 --> 29:16.753
by the angry spirit
of the old man.

29:17.455 --> 29:19.222
The house was sold
several times,

29:19.224 --> 29:21.525
but each time the
residents were driven out

29:22.427 --> 29:26.697
by the horrible gasping
breaths of the old man's ghost

29:26.699 --> 29:29.766
and the hideous blood stain
that could never be removed.

29:30.468 --> 29:35.539
The house was eventually
abandoned until just last year.

29:36.641 --> 29:38.542
One year ago today, in fact.

29:39.043 --> 29:45.349
When it was completely remodeled
and turned into Tearlon lodge.

29:48.087 --> 29:49.753
You're so full of it, Dale.

29:50.254 --> 29:51.688
I had you going.

29:51.690 --> 29:53.824
I don't know. I thought
the story was pretty good.

29:53.826 --> 29:57.694
Up until the end because I
think I heard that one before.

29:57.696 --> 29:58.895
Yeah?

29:59.464 --> 30:01.398
Good one, d, although I think

30:01.400 --> 30:03.266
you've got to give
partial credit to Joel.

30:03.268 --> 30:04.835
The wine definitely helped.

30:04.837 --> 30:06.536
Yeah, it's something else.

30:07.472 --> 30:08.472
You have any more?

30:08.474 --> 30:08.872
Yeah.

30:08.874 --> 30:11.274
I got a whole case of it.
I'll go get you some some more.

30:11.276 --> 30:12.709
