30:17.215 --> 30:19.649
He said don't be a bitch, bitch.

30:21.453 --> 30:23.220
Did you want any more?

30:23.222 --> 30:24.354
- Sure.
- Okay.

30:30.461 --> 30:31.328
Dale?

30:32.263 --> 30:33.163
Hey.

30:33.264 --> 30:34.831
You missed my finale.

30:34.833 --> 30:36.833
I'm sure you didn't disappoint.

30:36.835 --> 30:38.668
Yeah, but every
great storyteller

30:38.670 --> 30:41.805
saves his best for last.

30:41.807 --> 30:44.274
I'm worried about Rita.

30:44.276 --> 30:47.277
She hasn't come back yet
and she's been gone all day.

30:47.279 --> 30:48.378
Did you try her cell?

30:48.380 --> 30:50.313
No, I can't get a signal.

30:50.315 --> 30:51.715
Yeah, me either.

30:51.717 --> 30:53.250
Has anybody seen Rita?

30:53.252 --> 30:54.317
Yeah, I did.

30:54.319 --> 30:56.253
She got eaten by a bear.

30:56.255 --> 30:56.653
Tedi.

30:56.655 --> 30:59.189
Can you be serious
for one fucking minute?

30:59.191 --> 31:00.424
No.

31:01.193 --> 31:03.160
Which one's Rita again?

31:03.162 --> 31:07.431
She's a dark hair, skinny
chick, huge bug in her ass.

31:07.433 --> 31:08.298
Oh, yeah.

31:08.300 --> 31:09.666
I remember her.

31:09.668 --> 31:11.668
Yo, money bags, pass the hammer.

31:11.670 --> 31:13.437
Thank you.

31:13.439 --> 31:15.639
I really think we
should look for her.

31:15.641 --> 31:16.706
Wait a second.

31:16.708 --> 31:18.175
She comes up here all the time.

31:18.177 --> 31:20.243
She might have just gone to
visit with the caretaker.

31:20.245 --> 31:22.813
Well, is there any
way we can contact him?

31:22.815 --> 31:24.381
I don't think he
even has a phone.

31:24.383 --> 31:26.783
I kind of get the impression he
prefers to live off the grid.

31:27.485 --> 31:29.019
Well, what if Zac and
I go and look for her?

31:29.021 --> 31:29.419
No.

31:29.421 --> 31:32.622
I can't have you two traipsing
off in the middle of the night.

31:32.624 --> 31:34.458
You could get lost, or
fall in a bear trap,

31:34.460 --> 31:37.294
or god knows what else.

31:37.296 --> 31:39.529
If she's not back by the
morning we'll go look for her.

31:39.531 --> 31:41.298
- Okay?
- Alright.

31:41.300 --> 31:43.667
That goes for everybody.

31:43.669 --> 31:45.335
Even Joel?

31:45.337 --> 31:49.072
Yes, even Joel.

31:49.074 --> 31:51.208
With that, I'm going to
get some sleep.

31:51.210 --> 31:53.376
This wine's done a number on me.

31:53.378 --> 31:55.412
I need to hit the hay.

31:55.414 --> 31:57.814
Try to keep it down
to a dull roar.

31:57.816 --> 31:59.182
Good night, Dale.

31:59.184 --> 32:00.283
Night, bud.

32:00.285 --> 32:01.151
Goodnight.

32:01.153 --> 32:01.851
Night.

32:01.853 --> 32:05.088
Good night. I'm glad
you liked the wine.

32:05.090 --> 32:08.458
Well, can I refreshen
your glass, your majesty?

32:08.460 --> 32:10.660
Please.

32:10.662 --> 32:12.262
Whoa, that's good. Thank you.

32:12.264 --> 32:13.697
You're welcome.

32:13.699 --> 32:15.465
Here, babe.

32:15.467 --> 32:17.334
Seriously, Joel, enough.

32:19.303 --> 32:21.071
You're no good to me
when you're like this.

32:21.073 --> 32:22.205
Oh, come on.

32:22.207 --> 32:24.074
It's better when you're drunk.

32:24.076 --> 32:25.609
Not for me it's not.

32:25.611 --> 32:26.710
Whoa.

32:26.712 --> 32:29.079
Tough woman to please, huh?

32:29.081 --> 32:31.681
Buddy, you ain't kidding.

32:33.418 --> 32:34.718
I'm going to my room.

32:40.424 --> 32:42.125
Are you coming?

32:43.227 --> 32:46.730
Joel, the heart wants
what the heart wants.

32:47.832 --> 32:49.499
Not you, mongoloid.

32:49.501 --> 32:51.234
I'll be up in a minute, babe.

32:51.236 --> 32:52.369
Yeah. Fuck you.

32:54.672 --> 32:56.506
I'd get up there if I were you.

32:56.508 --> 32:58.508
