32:58.809 --> 33:02.546
The bitchier she gets.

33:03.080 --> 33:05.515
Too much to drink, Tedi boy.

33:06.250 --> 33:07.150
All right.

33:07.152 --> 33:09.352
Well, on that note.

33:10.454 --> 33:12.455
All right. I'll see
you guys later.

33:12.457 --> 33:15.458
Adios, amigos and, uh, feel free
to drink the rest of the wine.

33:15.460 --> 33:16.660
- Thank you.
- It's all yours.

33:16.662 --> 33:17.494
Good night.

33:17.496 --> 33:19.496
No. Wait, oh god.

33:19.498 --> 33:21.131
I'm going to join you.

33:22.433 --> 33:24.067
Oh, oh.

33:24.069 --> 33:25.168
I got you.

33:25.170 --> 33:26.169
I got you, big boy.

33:26.171 --> 33:27.537
Okay.

33:27.539 --> 33:28.638
There we go.

33:28.640 --> 33:29.138
Up the stairs.

33:29.140 --> 33:31.641
Hey, do you and lira
have any plans tonight?

33:31.643 --> 33:32.041
Yeah.

33:32.043 --> 33:36.079
I'm going to bury my sword so
deep in that stone-cold bitch,

33:36.081 --> 33:38.248
the first person who pulls it
out's going to get declared

33:38.250 --> 33:39.449
the king of England.

33:39.451 --> 33:40.717
Brothers.

33:41.652 --> 33:43.820
What are you two
jibber jabbering about?

33:43.822 --> 33:46.256
Just, just guy talk.

33:48.660 --> 33:50.093
Got you, buddy. Careful.

33:50.095 --> 33:52.562
Someone's going to break
their neck on those things.

33:52.564 --> 33:54.431
Yeah, watch out.

33:54.433 --> 33:56.466
Tedi, isn't your
room downstairs?

33:56.468 --> 33:59.302
I thought we were going to tag
team like the Hardy boys?

33:59.704 --> 34:02.272
No three way for you tonight,
bud. Sorry.

34:02.274 --> 34:03.740
