34:20.225 --> 34:21.491
Yeah. I'm going to go.

34:21.493 --> 34:22.559
Good choice.

34:22.827 --> 34:26.563
You, uh, slay that
fire-breathing cocksucker.

34:27.231 --> 34:28.130
