to get some action tonight.

34:50.522 --> 34:52.054
Good night, Tedi.

34:52.824 --> 34:54.157
Please.

34:54.159 --> 34:55.257
Good night. Go.

34:55.260 --> 34:56.426
Fine.

34:56.428 --> 34:59.362
