35:24.122 --> 35:25.522
I'm always right.

35:26.457 --> 35:27.891
How could I forget?

35:28.492 --> 35:29.526
It happens.

35:38.469 --> 35:42.272
Um, you gonna come upstairs?

35:42.274 --> 35:43.573
Not yet.

35:44.442 --> 35:46.343
I'm going to wait
here for a while.

35:46.644 --> 35:49.145
See if Rita straggles in.

35:51.248 --> 35:52.182
All right.

35:59.457 --> 36:01.191
Don't stay up all night.

36:01.459 --> 36:02.559
I won't.

36:03.661 --> 36:05.362
Good night, Zac.

36:06.097 --> 36:07.564
Good night, Meigan.

36:39.296 --> 36:40.330
Rita?

36:42.666 --> 36:43.566
Rita?

36:48.272 --> 36:49.572
Are you in here?

36:50.074 --> 36:51.107
Rita?

37:18.637 --> 37:19.702
What was that?

37:19.704 --> 37:21.471
Shut up, Joel.

37:21.473 --> 37:22.839
Yeah.

37:22.841 --> 37:24.774
