39:44.916 --> 39:45.414
Scare you?

39:45.416 --> 39:48.084
You're the one creeping
around in the fucking attic.

39:48.086 --> 39:49.652
I thought Hugo had gotten loose.

39:49.654 --> 39:51.454
I was halfway down
to the bait shop

39:51.456 --> 39:53.256
to pick up a bucket
of fish heads.

39:53.258 --> 39:54.257
Sorry.

39:54.259 --> 39:55.692
Hey, are you going
to come to bed?

39:55.694 --> 39:57.660
Think the fuck-a-thon
next door is over,

39:57.662 --> 40:00.063
so you and I actually
might get some sleep.

40:00.065 --> 40:02.365
Finally, some good news.

40:02.833 --> 40:05.301
What the hell are you
doing in the attic anyway?

40:08.105 --> 40:09.372
